34
00:02:19,873 --> 00:02:23,043 line:-1
on Mac for your app.


35
00:02:23,076 --> 00:02:25,979 line:-2
I'm going to start
with a couple of new options


36
00:02:26,013 --> 00:02:29,550 line:-1
for running your iOS app natively on M1,


37
00:02:29,583 --> 00:02:33,954 line:-2
the easiest way
